# Formspree - for contact form to send emails to chetan.karanjkar@gmail.com
# 1. Go to https://formspree.io and sign up (free)
# 2. Create a new form, set recipient to chetan.karanjkar@gmail.com
# 3. Copy your form ID from the URL (e.g. https://formspree.io/f/abc123xy -> abc123xy)
# 4. Rename this file to .env.local and add:
VITE_FORMSPREE_FORM_ID=your_form_id_here
